OL,4,G1750FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GOutspoken hairdresser Patrick
OL,6,     Gserves beef Wellington, but guest
OL,7,     GSharon finds him annoying.
OL,8,G1825FFour in a Bed
OL,9,     GDo the B&Bers like to be beside
OL,10,     Gthe seaside? First host Andy
OL,11,     Ghopes so at his guesthouse -
OL,12,     GSefton Blackpool - where he's
OL,13,     Glaying on a day of arcades and
OL,14,     Gice cream on the beach.
OL,15,G1855FFour in a Bed
OL,16,     GThe B&Bers have an udderly good
OL,17,     Gtime getting to grips with a very
OL,18,     Gunusual cow during a visit to
OL,19,     GCharlotte and Matt's glampsite,
OL,20,     GThe Apple Farm in Snitterfield,
OL,21,     GWarwickshire.
