OL,4,G1925FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GKaren and Bryan want to give
OL,6,     Gtheir guests fever - cabin fever
OL,7,     Gthat is! They're immensely proud
OL,8,     Gof their luxury lodges - Bechan
OL,9,     GRetreats in Powys. But will their
OL,10,     Gguests love them too?
OL,11,G1955FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GTensions are already bubbling
OL,13,     Gaway between the B&Bers before
OL,14,     Gthey've even arrived at Ying and
OL,15,     GJean's Castle Inn, in Powys. But
OL,16,     Gthe hosts have the answer to
OL,17,     Grestore harmony: pies.
